reviewText: This DVD is an adventure of Puss in Boots and is a delightful spin off from the Shrek movies.  The Three Diablos is about 3 kittens that Puss in Boots shows how to deal with life.
Title: Puss in Boots / The Three Diablos

reviewText: I took my four year old daughter to see this in the theatre and then bought it for her (with the additional Diablos DVD as well) when it was released. She loved it! The story could have definitely been stronger, but it is a very sweet movie and the music and dancing is fun and enjoyable. Many animated movies include adults just as much as they do the kids, and while I can't say that 100% for this movie, it was entertaining enough for the whole family.
Title: Puss in Boots / The Three Diablos
